pullRequest.body:
* Search + replace `em‚Ñíp` by `emLp`
* Automatically added deprecations (roughly) by using the regex replace `(theorem|lemma|def) ([^ \n]*)emLp([^ \n]*)(((?!\n\n)[\s\S])*)$` >
```
$1 $2emLp$3$4

@[deprecated (since := "2025-02-21")] 
alias $2emùìõp$3 := $2emLp$3
```
* Undid unwanted alias replaces by `alias ([^ ]*)emLp([^ ]*)` > `alias $1emùìõp$2` (but had to manually change some aliases back that were not deprecated)
* A few lemmas use `ùìõp` to refer to `eLpNorm`, which are now renamed to use `eLpNorm`

---
